Our accommodations

   The new ibis room is modern, welcoming and comfortable with the Sweet
   Bed by ibis bed and mattress topper, mobile furniture, large TV,
   multi-plug and USB, A/C and functional bathroom for the best stay in
   the heart of Lille!
