   TripAdvisor Certificate of Excellence Certificate of excellence 2019

   Exceeded all expectations
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Anonymous Solo - 17/09/2019 AccorHotels review

   Over delivered in every respect. Close to airport, very clean,
   efficient staff and check in / out. Best of all I left at 4.30 am for
   an early flight. Breakfast shouldn't have been until 5am, but the
   overnight staff had it fully ready well before this time - full buffet,
   including an orange juice machine. Great experience. Taxi is 15E when
   shuttle isn't running.
   Dear ANDREW G., We very much appreciate your comments regarding your
   stay at the ibis Styles Bordeaux Aéroport. It is always a pleasure to
   receive positive feedback. I will share your comments with our team. I
   am sure that this feedback will serve as an encouragement to all of our
   staff as we strive to continuously improve the quality of our services.
   Thank you again for sharing your experience, and we hope your next
   visit will be as pleasant as the previous one. Sincerely, Loïc Artiga
   General Manager

   Very good experience overall
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Time B. Families - 11/09/2019 AccorHotels review

   Overall pretty good. (+) Accommodation was roomy Staff was helpful. One
   lady packed some croissants for us a we were leaving early. Well
   insulated, no noise coming from outside, which is important when you
   stay close to an airport the complementary water bottles were nice to
   have (-) Minor: we had a 7am flight and I wished the shuttle was
   available on demand. we took the bus. that still worked out though the
   shower does not have any door so there is water splashing in the room

