   Excellent hotel with all amenities on site.
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Soizick M. Solo - 17/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   I had never stayed in a Ibis Styles although I am familiar with the
   AccorHotels group. I needed a small room for one night before a flight
   and was very nicely surprised by Ibis Styles. It was comfortable, the
   staff was friendly and on top of that there was a restaurant with great
   food! A shuttle took me in the morning. Perfect! I recommend it!

   Satisfactory, but with a significant flaw.
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Nigel R. Couples - 14/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   In general it was good....... adequate room, pleasant and helpful staff
   and a satisfactory breakfast. But when I booked I asked especially
   about whether the restaurant would be open on the evening of our
   arrival. I was told it would be. When my wife and I checked-in we were
   warned it was shut. We were advised to got to a pub/brasserie along the
   road, not a long walk, but a difficult one for Mrs R. who has an
   injured knee. I must also mention that the ‘navette’ link with the
   airport was very useful.

   Older hotel with poor transfer service to the airport.
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Dennis H. Couples - 12/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   The room was clean. However, having your transfer service to the
   airport starting at 7 am was inadequate. There are many flights that
   are scheduled early in the morning. Our flight was scheduled for 6am.
   Very disappointing. A few days earlier we were at an Ibis hotel in
   Basel-Mulhouse. Their shuttle service started at 4am.

   Excellent, beyond my expectations
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Kerry Families - 11/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   Friendly staff. Lovely communal area, plus small outdoor space. Great,
   large breakfast. Room was fine, quiet and good bathroom. You can walk
   from the airport, 10 mins

   Great value hotel close to the airport
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Cathy Friends - 06/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   My initial allocated room had a squashed up brown paper bag on the
   floor. It also smelt very strongly of cigarettes and was very hot, as
   the aircon didn't work. I immediately went to the front desk to
   complain, and was moved to another room that was great.

   Good value one night stay
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Andrea Solo - 06/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   Generally good. Unfortunately there was no shuttle bus available when I
   landed which wasn't a great start. Then I had to walk through a line of
   smokers to get into reception. Room was clean, and the complimentary
   water appreciated. Breakfast was very good, as were check in and out.
   Shuttle back to airport was good.

   Everything one needs
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Jennifer G. Friends - 04/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   Quick shuttle, check in. Comfortable room. Adequate breakfast. Fast
   check out.

   Great family rooms!
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Sarah P. Families - 04/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   Friendly and efficient staff who kindly gave my children a gift and
   left sweets in our room for them too. Plenty of space in the family
   room, divided by a sliding door and useful air-con. TVs in both the
   children's side and the adults'. Good shower and plenty of towels
   provided. All clean and tidy. The buffet breakfast has lots to choose
   from including delicious freshly squeezed orange juice and eggs to
   boil. Croissants and pain au chocolat are left for guests in the
   communal area where they can also make tea -a great idea! There is a
   lovely play area for children. We stayed here twice in July 2019
   (before and after our holiday) and were really pleased.

   Good for overnight stay
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Francist Couples - 03/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   For one night good however dinner and breakfast were excellent

   Great comfortable location
   Customer review rating 4.3/5

   Anonymous Solo - 03/08/2019 AccorHotels review

   Great location to airport. Clean comfortable accommodation. Pleasant
   efficient staff and good amenities.
